Opinion 'YOU FINISHED ME OFF' Tragic last words of 25-year-old woman decapitated and stabbed to death by jealous boyfriend in ‘sadistic’ murder recorded on phone 
Alin Apopei, 27, repeatedly threatened to kill sex worker Denisa Silmen, 25, before she was found brutally murdered at their east London flat by sam christie
